{"text_id":127778,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," present"," the"," construction"," of"," Bayesian"," deforma","ble"," models"," via"," a"," stochastic"," approximation"," algorithm",","," accompanied"," by"," a"," comprehensive"," convergence"," analysis","."," The"," motivation"," for"," our"," research"," lies"," in"," addressing"," the"," limitations"," of"," traditional"," deforma","ble"," models",","," which"," often"," require"," the"," specification"," of"," a"," fixed",","," hand","-","crafted"," set"," of"," parameters","."," By"," contrast",","," our"," proposed"," Bayesian"," modeling"," framework"," allows"," for"," the"," incorporation"," of"," prior"," knowledge"," and"," the"," automatic"," adaptation"," of"," model"," parameters"," through"," data","-","driven"," inference",".","\n\n","The"," methodology"," consists"," of"," two"," main"," components","."," First",","," we"," employ"," a"," stochastic"," approximation"," algorithm"," to"," update"," the"," model"," parameters"," by"," iter","atively"," evaluating"," the"," posterior"," distribution","."," Second",","," we"," prove"," the"," convergence"," of"," this"," algorithm",","," providing"," a"," theoretical"," foundation"," for"," the"," proposed"," approach","."," Our"," results"," demonstrate"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," the"," proposed"," framework"," in"," various"," scenarios",","," including"," image"," registration"," and"," shape"," analysis",".","\n\n","The"," proposed"," algorithm"," exhibits"," several"," advantages","."," First",","," it"," alle","vi","ates"," the"," need"," for"," carefully"," selecting"," model"," parameters",","," allowing"," for"," more"," robust"," and"," accurate"," modeling"," of"," complex"," structures","."," Second",","," it"," provides"," a"," consistent"," framework"," for"," incorporating"," prior"," knowledge"," and"," uncertainty"," in"," the"," modeling"," process","."," Finally",","," the"," stochastic"," approximation"," algorithm"," offers"," computational"," efficiency"," by"," avoiding"," the"," need"," to"," evaluate"," high","-","dimensional"," integrals","."," In"," conclusion",","," this"," study"," presents"," a"," novel"," Bayesian"," deforma","ble"," modeling"," framework",","," combining"," the"," merits"," of"," stochastic"," approximation"," and"," Bayesian"," inference"," for"," deforma","ble"," model"," construction"," and"," providing"," a"," solid"," theoretical"," foundation"," for"," its"," convergence","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}